class Solution(object):
    def compareVersion(self, version1, version2):
        """
        :type version1: str
        :type version2: str
        :rtype: int
        """
        v1 = version1.split('.')
        v2 = version2.split('.')
        maxLevel = max(len(v1), len(v2))

        for i in range(maxLevel):
            d1 = int(v1[i]) if i < len(v1) else 0
            d2 = int(v2[i]) if i < len(v2) else 0

            if d1 > d2:
                return 1
            elif d1 < d2:
                return -1
        return 0
